We must begin a new phase of European construction.
To establish a republic in France, we had to "create" the Republicans.
A revolution of interests would not be enough.
This lesson remains valid.
We must build a Europe united on an economic level.
This can be done only through the creation of a more democratic Europe at the political level, a genuine popular European sovereignty.
To create Europe, let us create Europeans.
